params.amountEigenToDeposit: amount of eigen token to deposit
params.operatorIndex: is the index of the operator to use from the test-data/operators.json file

params.eigenToDeposit: is amount of eigen to deposit into the eigen strategy

params.numStratsToAdd: is the number of strategies being added and deposited into

params.amountToDeposit: Fuzzed input for amount of WETH to deposit

_testInitiateDelegation(uint8,uint256,ui.notice: Helper function to test `initiateDelegation` functionality.  Handles registering as an operator, depositing tokens into both Weth and Eigen strategies, as well as delegating assets from "stakers" to the operator.

testDepositEigen(uint96).notice: Verifies that it is possible to deposit eigen.

testDepositNonexistentStrategy(address).notice: Tries to deposit into an unsupported strategy by calling `strategyManager.depositIntoStrategy`. Verifies that reversion occurs correctly.

testDepositStrategies(uint8).notice: deploys 'numStratsToAdd' strategies using '_testAddStrategy' and then deposits '1e18' to each of them from 'getOperatorAddress(0)'

testDepositUnsupportedToken().notice: Tries to deposit an unsupported token into an `StrategyBase` contract by calling `strategyManager.depositIntoStrategy`. Verifies that reversion occurs correctly.

testForkMainnetDepositSteth().notice: Shadow-forks mainnet and tests depositing stETH tokens into a "StrategyBase" contract.

testRevertOnZeroDeposit().notice: verify that trying to deposit an amount of zero will correctly revert

testWethDeposit(uint256).notice: Verifies that it is possible to deposit WETH
